{
  "stem": "3360.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The American government had quotas for every country, whereby you were assigned a quota number.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unless it was a country like, say, Denmark or Sweden, where there weren't so many people that were dying to get out of there-- but a quota number is what you needed to get from the American government.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They needed to see if your-- if your affidavit was in order and correct-- and which they finally had-- my uncle finally had sent.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think that he had sent it before the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- excuse me-- and-- because the waiting period at that time-- because so many more Jews were really trying to get out, the waiting period was about a year.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So a year would have taken us to July or August of 1938 that we would have had to present it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't recall it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I do recall going to the American Embassy, while you're bringing it up-- not the embassy, the Consulate, and, and undergoing a very undignified physical examination.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I'm not-- I'm not going to go into details of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Hamburg-- the American Consulate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, we had this quota number assigned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a wait over here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was fearful that, in a year's time, things would be so much worse, that everybody would be hauled off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- however, that did not come about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were lucky that we were still all in one piece by the time it was time for us to book a passage on a-- on a liner to cross the Atlantic.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was going to say something else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now what was it?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
